        aim <target's name>

Aiming is the first step in typical ranged combat.  The command is issued in
the following format:

  aim <name> <direction>

...Thus, i.e.  "aim guard north" would target a guard to the north.  The target
is typically found using the "scan" or "look <direction>" commands, although 
aim can be used upon someone present in the same room as the player using the
format:

