CONSIDER

Usage:  consider <target>

A wise warrior always carefully considers his or her foe before entering
combat.  This command will compare your total point value with that of the
target's. You will receive a rough estimate of their toughness in combat,
which is by no means exact.  Point value may or may not be relevant to actual
difficulty in combat.
