BASH

Usage:  bash [target] or set in combat profile

Speed: 10

A bashing attack attempts to knock the target over.  Success is affected by
the weight of the attacker and target, and the heavier of the two will have an
advantage.  If the attack succeeds, the victim will be knocked to the ground;
otherwise, the attacker will themselves tumble to the ground and be unable to
attack.

A shield may be worn and used for the "shield bash", which enhances both the 
chance of success and the damage of a bashing attack.

While in combat, the target is assumed to be the character's opponent if not 
specified.

See also:  SHIELDBASH
