SKILLS

Skills are the rating of what your character knows and is capable of.  Next to
stats, they are the most important attribute of a character.  Both players and
computer-controlled characters gain skills over time through usage.

Because Tower of the Lost Order does not rely strictly on class or level to
define a character's abilities, skills and the attributes they rely on are the
